prompt:
Nurse: Hi, this is Rachel calling from O'Connor Hospital. I'm an AI on a recorded line. Is this Alex Gates?

Patient: Yes.

Nurse: Hello. I'm calling on behalf of your primary care doctor, Doctor Jami Wyatt, to check in on you. How have you been doing lately?

Patient: I'm in okay.

Nurse: I'm sorry, Alex, I didn't quite catch that. Could you please repeat how you've been feeling lately?

Patient: Okay.

Nurse: I'm glad to hear that you're doing okay. Is there anything you're looking forward to doing this week?

Patient: Just spending time with my family.

responses.gpt4: That sounds lovely. Family time is very important. Should you have any health concerns, don't hesitate to reach out to your doctor. Have a nice day!
responses.our_model: That sounds lovely. Family time is always special. Are there any specific activities you enjoy doing with your family?
